(9, '1', '5', 'Ecotact Launches a Recycling and Sustainable Initiative', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The word sustainable in its very dictionary meaning refers to “conserving an ecological balance by avoiding depletion of natural resources.” Over the years this balance has been tattered and our environment is now under great threat. The United Nations along with other social enterprises and research organizations have stepped forward in educating people about the adversities of our environment and the growing need to adopt more environment friendly and ecologically sustainable lifestyle. As a part of the 2030 agenda, UN has adopted few measures and emphasizes a holistic approach to achieving sustainable development for all for a sustainable growth.</span></p><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: table;\"><img src=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/UN-1024x187.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-160\" width=\"368\" height=\"67\" srcset=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/UN-1024x187.png 1024w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/UN-300x55.png 300w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/UN-768x141.png 768w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/UN-1200x220.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 85vw, 368px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; display: block; width: 368px; height: auto;\"></figure></div><ul style=\"margin: 23px 0px 34px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; list-style: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; position: relative;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">By 2030, upgrade infrastructure and retrofit industries to make them sustainable, with increased resource-use efficiency and greater adoption of clean and environmentally sound technologies and industrial processes, with all countries taking action in accordance with their respective capabilities</span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; position: relative;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Improve progressively, through 2030, global resource efficiency in consumption and production and endeavor to decouple economic growth from environmental degradation, in accordance with the 10-year framework of programs on sustainable consumption and production, with developed countries taking the lead</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Many environmental scientists are of the view that unless over-consumption of resources is stopped, modern civilization will collapse just like ancient civilizations that didn’t apply sustainable use of their resources.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">We believe that each effort counts and is a step towards a greener future. Owing to our environment and taking a pledge to protect it, Ecotact is committed to a sustainable and green trade. Being in the DNA of the organization, Ecotact believes in reducing the carbon footprint and saving the environment for a better future. To this end, Ecotact has joined hands with different agencies in different parts of the world to manage waste effectively and very recently launched an initiative to recycle its hermetic bags.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">How does it work?</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ecotact Food grade Multilayered Hermetic Plastic bags are 100% recyclable. As a responsible global organization, we believe in sustainability and circular economy. We have invested not only in creating products that are reliable and responsible but also by creating recycling processes, which enables every single user of our product to be a part of the global movement of reducing carbon footprints. We have created a global infrastructure with a one-stop shop for collection and actual recycling of Ecotact products. We have global partners in various parts of the world who help us to collect and recycle them at a negligible or no cost to the user.</span></p><div class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: table;\"><img src=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/TerraCycle-Order-Instructions-1024x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-157\" srcset=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/TerraCycle-Order-Instructions-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/TerraCycle-Order-Instructions-300x150.jpg 300w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/TerraCycle-Order-Instructions-768x384.jpg 768w, https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/Terra