(10, '2', '5', 'Ecotact Lanza Una Iniciativa de Reciclaje y Sostenibilidad', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">La palabra sostenible de acuerdo a su significado del diccionario se refiere a \"conservar un equilibrio ecol&oacute;gico evitando el agotamiento de los recursos naturales\". A lo largo de los a&ntilde;os este equilibrio se ha ido rompiendo y nuestro medio ambiente est&aacute; ahora muy amenazado. Las Naciones Unidas, junto con otras empresas sociales y organizaciones de investigaci&oacute;n, han dado un paso adelante para educar a la gente sobre las adversidades de nuestro entorno y la creciente necesidad de adoptar un estilo de vida m&aacute;s respetuoso con el medio ambiente y ecol&oacute;gicamente sostenible. Como parte de la agenda 2030, la ONU ha adoptado algunas medidas y hace hincapi&eacute; en un enfoque hol&iacute;stico para lograr un desarrollo sostenible para todos para un crecimiento sostenible.</span></p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n    <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Para 2030, mejorar las infraestructuras y modernizar las industrias para hacerlas sostenibles, con una mayor eficiencia en el uso de los recursos y una mayor adopci&oacute;n de tecnolog&iacute;as y procesos industriales limpios y respetuosos con el medio ambiente, tomando todos los pa&iacute;ses medidas de acuerdo con sus respectivas capacidades</span></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /><br /></span></p>\r\n    <ul>\r\n    <li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mejorar progresivamente, hasta 2030, la eficiencia global de los recursos en el consumo y la producci&oacute;n y esforzarse por desvincular el crecimiento econ&oacute;mico de la degradaci&oacute;n medioambiental, en un marco de diez a&ntilde;os y de acuerdo con los programas existentes sobre consumo y producci&oacute;n sostenibles, con los pa&iacute;ses desarrollados a la cabeza.</span></li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Muchos cient&iacute;ficos medioambientales opinan que, si no se frena el consumo excesivo de recursos, la civilizaci&oacute;n moderna se derrumbar&aacute; al igual que las antiguas civilizaciones que no aplicaron un uso sostenible de sus recursos.</span></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creemos que cada esfuerzo cuenta y es un paso hacia un futuro m&aacute;s verde. Debido a nuestro entorno y asumiendo el compromiso de protegerlo, Ecotact se compromete con un comercio sostenible y ecol&oacute;gico. Al estar en el ADN de la organizaci&oacute;n, Ecotact cree en la reducci&oacute;n de la huella de carbono y en la conservaci&oacute;n del medio ambiente para un futuro mejor. Con este fin, Ecotact se ha aliado con diferentes organismos en distintas partes del mundo para gestionar los residuos de forma eficaz y, muy recientemente, ha lanzado una iniciativa para reciclar sus bolsas herm&eacute;ticas.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;C&oacute;mo funciona?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Las bolsas de pl&aacute;stico herm&eacute;tico multicapa de Ecotact son 100% reciclables. Como organizaci&oacute;n global responsable, creemos en la sostenibilidad y la econom&iacute;a circular. Hemos invertido no s&oacute;lo en la creaci&oacute;n de productos confiables y responsables, sino tambi&eacute;n en la creaci&oacute;n de procesos de reciclaje, lo que permite a cada uno de los usuarios de nuestro producto formar parte del movimiento global de reducci&oacute;n de la huella de carbono. Hemos creado una infraestructura global con una ventanilla &uacute;nica para la recogida y el reciclaje real de los productos Ecotact. Tenemos socios globales en varias partes del mundo que nos ayudan a recogerlos y reciclarlos a un coste insignificante o nulo para el usuario.</span></p>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p><strong>Pasos para pedir su caja de reciclaje Ecotact</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&iexcl;Env&iacute;enos su caja rellena para su reciclaje! Seamos un habitante responsable y adoptemos m&eacute;todos de reciclaje para preservar nuestro medio ambiente en los a&ntilde;os venideros. Para m&aacute;s informaci&oacute;n, haga clic aqu&iacute;.</span></p>', '2020-09-26', '2021-04-29 11:47:47', '2021-06-29 06:07:50'),
(11, '1', '6', 'Honey Processing and Natural Processing of Green Coffee Using Ecotact', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">There are various kinds of&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">processing of green coffee</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, natural and honey being the most complex amongst them. This blog aims at reinstating information for proper understanding of the processes. One might wonder what exactly are these and how does one go about the process? Well here’s a comprehensive explanation to quench your brewing curiosity.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Natural process</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, also known as the&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">dry process</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, is a basic process that originated in&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Ethiopia</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">. It is processed by leaving fruit on the bean, with little to no disruption while it dries. Although it needs less investment, it still requires certain climatic conditions to ensure the drying of the fruit and seed in time.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The harvesting process is very demanding for the production of&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Specialty grade Naturals</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, since the mass must be extremely homogeneous, to warrant a product with the adequate taste and conditions. The drying process implies an organized and scientific process, where the percentages of humidity and weight are recorded until coffees reach the ideal point and are stored away. Different than the washed coffee, the Natural coffee has metabolic activity along the time and stored where principally fungus, allows for a better quality of the beans, since this metabolism provides the green beans with better precursors of flavor and smell for the roasters to work with. This process has the potential to create the most flavorful coffees.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">That is why stored Naturals, have a tendency to have more complex and pleasant flavors after 4-6 months of storage inside&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">ECOTACT</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;bags.</span></p><div class=\"singlePostWrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><div class=\"singlePostImg\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 33px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">On the other hand,&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Honey processed coffee</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;are halfway between a washed coffee and a natural process coffee. The name actually comes from how sticky the beans get during processing. It’s fruity, but not in as exaggerated a way as some naturals. It often has a more rounded acidity than washed coffees, with intense sweetness and complex mouth feel.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">They have a less complex selection process, since the window of opportunity for harvesting is a little bit less narrow; unfortunately Honey coffees are more&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">complex to produce</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, since the variability of the environmental conditions can affect the consistency of that type of process in a more dramatic way.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The Honey coffee is put to dry without washing the mucilage, making the parchment stained and conferring the name of the coffee from black to red to blonde etc. Once the coffee has been dried,&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">storage inside ECOTACT bags</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;will allow for&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">further metabolic activity</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, again related to fungus (beneficial) that with time will enhance the availability of flavor and smell precursors that will enhance the coffee for the roaster to express.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Use as a store system for Parchment right at the farm, we recommend our producers to keep their properly dried coffees inside&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">ECOTACT bags</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;to&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">prevent re-absorption of water and oxygen exposure</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, and extend quality and survival time for their crops.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 28px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Coffee processing is an integral part of the industry but is rarely spoken about. It is the most important step for the</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">&nbsp;best flavor</strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">brewing in your cup every morning.</span></strong></p></div></div><div id=\"comments\" class=\"commentsBox\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 80px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><h3 id=\"comments\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(11, 11, 11); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">ONE RESPONSE TO “HONEY PROCESSING AND NATURAL PROCESSING OF GREEN COFFEE USING ECOTACT”</span></h3></div>', '2020-09-22', '2021-04-29 11:49:08', '2021-06-22 08:07:20'),
(12, '2', '6', 'Procesamiento de Miel y Procesamiento Natural Del Café Verde con Ecotact', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Existen varios tipos de procesamiento del caf&eacute; verde, siendo el natural y el honey los m&aacute;s complejos. Este blog tiene como objetivo restablecer la informaci&oacute;n para la correcta comprensi&oacute;n de los procesos. Uno podr&iacute;a preguntarse qu&eacute; son exactamente y c&oacute;mo se lleva a cabo el proceso. A continuaci&oacute;n, le ofrecemos una explicaci&oacute;n exhaustiva para saciar su curiosidad. El proceso natural, tambi&eacute;n conocido como proceso seco, es un proceso b&aacute;sico que se origin&oacute; en Etiop&iacute;a. Se procesa dejando la fruta en el grano mientras este se seca. Aunque necesita menos inversi&oacute;n, sigue requiriendo ciertas condiciones clim&aacute;ticas para garantizar el secado del fruto y la semilla a tiempo. El proceso de recolecci&oacute;n es muy exigente para la producci&oacute;n de Specialty grade Naturals, ya que la masa debe ser extremadamente homog&eacute;nea, para garantizar un producto con el sabor y las condiciones adecuadas. El proceso de secado implica un proceso organizado y cient&iacute;fico, donde se registran los porcentajes de humedad y peso hasta que los caf&eacute;s alcanzan el punto ideal y se almacenan. A diferencia del caf&eacute; lavado, el caf&eacute; Natural tiene una actividad metab&oacute;lica a lo largo del tiempo y almacenado donde principalmente los hongos, son los que permiten una mejor calidad de los granos, ya que este metabolismo proporciona a los granos verdes mejores precursores de sabor y olor para que los tostadores trabajen con ellos. Este proceso tiene el potencial de crear los caf&eacute;s m&aacute;s sabrosos. Por eso los naturales almacenados, tienen tendencia a tener sabores m&aacute;s complejos y agradables despu&eacute;s de 4-6 meses de almacenamiento dentro de las bolsas ECOTACT.</span></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;Por otro lado, los caf&eacute;s procesados como semilavados est&aacute;n a medio camino entre un caf&eacute; lavado y un caf&eacute; de proceso natural. El nombre &ldquo;honey&rdquo; viene en realidad de lo pegajosos que se vuelven los granos durante el procesado. Es afrutado, pero no de forma tan exagerada como algunos naturales. Suele tener una acidez m&aacute;s balanceada con notas afrutadas maduras m&aacute;s que los caf&eacute;s lavados, con un dulzor intenso y una sensaci&oacute;n compleja en boca. Tienen un proceso de selecci&oacute;n menos complejo, ya que la ventana de oportunidad para la cosecha es un poco menos estrecha; desafortunadamente los caf&eacute;s honey son m&aacute;s complejos de producir, ya que la variabilidad de las condiciones ambientales puede afectar la consistencia de ese tipo de proceso de manera m&aacute;s dram&aacute;tica. El caf&eacute; honey se pone a secar sin lavar el muc&iacute;lago, haciendo que el pergamino se manche y confiriendo el nombre del caf&eacute; de negro a rojo a rubio, etc. Una vez que el caf&eacute; se ha secado, el almacenamiento dentro de las bolsas ECOTACT permitir&aacute; una mayor actividad metab&oacute;lica, de nuevo relacionada con los hongos (beneficiosa) que con el tiempo potenciar&aacute; la disponibilidad de precursores de sabor y olor que mejorar&aacute;n el caf&eacute; para que el tostador lo exprese. Como sistema de almacenamiento de Pergamino en la propia finca, recomendamos a nuestros productores que mantengan sus caf&eacute;s debidamente secados dentro de las bolsas ECOTACT para evitar la reabsorci&oacute;n de agua y la exposici&oacute;n al ox&iacute;geno, y extender la calidad y el tiempo de supervivencia de sus cosechas. El procesamiento del caf&eacute; es una parte integral de la industria, pero rara vez se habla de &eacute;l. Es el paso m&aacute;s importante para obtener el mejor sabor en su taza cada ma&ntilde;ana.</span></p>', '2020-09-22', '2021-04-29 11:49:08', '2021-06-22 08:07:20'),
(13, '1', '7', 'Exploring Facets of Coffee Production with Mr.Carlos Melen, Ceo, Good Coffee Farms', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">We spoke to Mr. Carlos Melen about various coffee production techniques while delving into the sustainability of these produces. We broadly spoke on 4 major topics around coffee production and gaining an industry insight from the industry expert himself. Let’s read along</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are the ecological benefits of dry bicycle de-pulping machine and how did it come about?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Well, back in those days I did not have enough money to buy one of those big industrial machines and those would cost a fortune because of the amount of water they would take up to peel the beans perfectly. Yes, according to the website of Specialty Coffee Association of United States, it specifies that for each kilogram of green beans that we produce through the regular machine, we are using 10,000 litres of water. This gave birth to my idea where we don’t use a single drop of water with this machine. That changes everything. Now with one of these devices we can produce 17 tonnes of green beans or let’s call it one container.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Do you use Brix meter for handpicking the right cherries?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">We use Brix meter twice to collect the cherries. We check the Brix sugar level at the farm, and then go for the collection, post which it takes up to 3 to 4 hours for them to take it to the mill, where we have the machines. Depending on the weather of the particular day, the coffee may change its color a bit. So we check again and depending on the result we decide, if we are going to do a wash process.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Tell us about your experience of growing coffee in Japan</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Japan has a lot more access to technology and methods. So, they have been applying their expertise in technology in coffee production too. What we trying to do is an exchange of information. Here in Japan, because of the landscape and the locations, the tropical climate and altitude, Japan is an emerging player in coffee business. But as much as they are turning into a global player they never compromise on quality. They go for quality with small quantities.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are your views on keeping green coffee intact with Ecotact?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ecotact bags are sustainable, economical and very importantly environment friendly. They keep the flavor of the beans intact thus prolonging the freshness and durability.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">How has your experience with Ecotact been?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">My experience with Ecotact is amazing. I think I have been doing a great job working as a promoter of Ecotact bags, because everywhere I go, I just mention about the bags and tell them you need to use bags like this because they will help you to either way keep, preserve or it could also help to improve the quality. Vacuum pack is very important to preserve and we have very good results with Ecotact bags. Depending on the quality of the coffee, and what the clients/customers wants, we pack with vacuum and put it in boxes and ship it by air.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Here’s our detailed&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLE9ETOZUJU\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(17, 102, 54); display: inline-block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">video interview</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;with Mr.Carlos Melen. Do give it a&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLE9ETOZUJU\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(17, 102, 54); display: inline-block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">watch</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">!&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>', '2020-09-25', '2021-05-10 14:11:02', '2021-08-19 19:15:03'),
(14, '2', '7', 'Explorando Las Facetas de La Producción de Café Con el Señor Carlos Melen- Director General de Good Coffee Farms', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hablamos con el Sr. Carlon Melen sobre diversas t&eacute;cnicas de producci&oacute;n de caf&eacute; y profundizamos en la sostenibilidad de estos productos. Hablamos ampliamente de 4 temas principales en torno a la producci&oacute;n de caf&eacute; y obtuvimos una visi&oacute;n de la industria por parte del propio experto en la materia. Sigamos leyendo</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Cu&aacute;les son los beneficios ecol&oacute;gicos de la despulpadora en seco y c&oacute;mo surgi&oacute;?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bueno, en aquella &eacute;poca no ten&iacute;a suficiente dinero para comprar una de esas grandes m&aacute;quinas industriales y &eacute;stas costaban una fortuna debido a la cantidad de agua que consum&iacute;an para pelar los granos perfectamente. S&iacute;, seg&uacute;n la p&aacute;gina web de la Asociaci&oacute;n de Caf&eacute;s Especiales de Estados Unidos, especifica que por cada kilo de granos verdes que producimos a trav&eacute;s de la m&aacute;quina normal, estamos utilizando 10.000 litros de agua. De ah&iacute; naci&oacute; mi idea de no utilizar ni una sola gota de agua con esta m&aacute;quina. Eso lo cambia todo. Ahora, con uno de estos aparatos podemos producir 17 toneladas de grano verdes o, digamos, un contenedor.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Utilizan el medidor de grados Brix para recoger las cerezas adecuadas?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Utilizamos el medidor de grados Brix dos veces para recoger las cerezas. Comprobamos el nivel de los grados Brix en la finca y luego vamos a recoger las cerezas de caf&eacute;, despu&eacute;s nos tarda entre 3 y 4 horas en llevarlas al molino, donde tenemos las m&aacute;quinas. Dependiendo del tiempo que haga ese d&iacute;a, el caf&eacute; puede cambiar un poco de color. As&iacute; que volvemos a comprobarlo y, en funci&oacute;n del resultado, decidimos si vamos a realizar un proceso de lavado.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>H&aacute;blenos de su experiencia en el cultivo de caf&eacute; en Jap&oacute;n</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jap&oacute;n tiene mucho m&aacute;s acceso a la tecnolog&iacute;a y a los m&eacute;todos. As&iacute; que han aplicado su experiencia en tecnolog&iacute;a tambi&eacute;n en la producci&oacute;n de caf&eacute;. Lo que intentamos hacer es un intercambio de informaci&oacute;n. Aqu&iacute;, en Jap&oacute;n, debido al paisaje y a las ubicaciones, al clima tropical y a la altitud, Jap&oacute;n es un actor emergente en el negocio del caf&eacute;. Pero, por mucho que se est&eacute; convirtiendo en un actor global, nunca compromete la calidad. Apuestan por la calidad con peque&ntilde;as cantidades.</span></p>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; opina de mantener el caf&eacute; verde intacto con Ecotact?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Las bolsas Ecotact son sostenibles, econ&oacute;micas y, lo que es m&aacute;s importante, respetuosas con el medio ambiente. Mantienen intacto el sabor de los granos, prolongando as&iacute; la frescura y la durabilidad.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;C&oacute;mo ha sido su experiencia con Ecotact?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mi experiencia con Ecotact es incre&iacute;ble. Creo que he hecho un gran trabajo como promotor de las bolsas Ecotact, porque dondequiera que voy, simplemente menciono las bolsas y les digo que necesitan usar bolsas como estas porque les ayudar&aacute;n a conservar, preservar o tambi&eacute;n podr&iacute;an ayudar a mejorar la calidad. El envasado al vac&iacute;o es muy importante para la conservaci&oacute;n y tenemos muy buenos resultados con las bolsas Ecotact. Dependiendo de la calidad del caf&eacute;, y de lo que quieran los clientes/consumidores, lo envasamos al vac&iacute;o y lo ponemos en cajas y lo enviamos por aire.</span></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aqu&iacute; est&aacute; nuestra detallada entrevista en v&iacute;deo con el Sr. Carlos Melen. No deje de verla.</span></p>', '2020-09-25', '2021-05-10 14:11:02', '2021-08-19 19:15:03');
INSERT INTO `language__blogs` (`id`, `language_id`, `blog_id`, `title`, `desc`, `date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(15, '1', '8', 'Conversations over Coffee with Hendra Taruli, Director,Opal Coffee', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">According to you what changes have taken place in the coffee industry due to COVID-19? Has it impacted the way Opal Coffee operates?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">COVID-19 has impacted Opal Coffee in many ways, in the way businesses are conducted. This includes various changes in the industry. Most buyers prefer sticking to their past buying methods. As volume is decreasing in the specialty segment, there has been an increase in the commercial segment. With changing times, the technology methods have sped up too.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Has this affected the demand for coffee in the past few months?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The volume has been decreasing in the specialty segment while there has been an increase in the commercial segment.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Opal Coffee operates globally. You have some markets that are moderately impacted and others that are largely impacted due to COVID19. How differently is the coffee market impacted in each of these regions? And the way forward.</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">COVID-19 has impacted differently, in particular to those businesses which have been hit heavily in their volume. As their fixed cost remains constant, most roasters would take the option of reducing cost of purchases, to increase their gross margin to pay fixed overheads.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Coffee Sourcing – How different is sourcing of coffee during these tough times when visit to origin is not possible. How differently is the industry sourcing specialty coffee?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">We have modified our previous methodologies and relationships that we have fostered. Suppliers are shipping the samples instead of us visiting the origin and consequently, there have been some delays in the decision-making process. We have used this time to build new relationships with our suppliers too, as earlier we never got a chance to do so.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What has been the impact on pricing of green coffee which was already at historically low levels?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The price has been fluctuating for a long time now and nothing much has affected the actual price.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Has currency depreciation of most of the producing countries helped the local farmers and exporters of coffee?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The currency depreciation has definitely affected the small manufacturers, but since currency depreciation is often reflected in NY market movement, the final price of delivery pretty much remains the same.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What points do you keep in mind for storing green coffee beans?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">When storing coffee one should always store it in a cool and dry place. Other than that it should be stored in&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><a href=\"https://ecotactbags.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Ecotact (opens in a new tab)\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(17, 102, 54); display: inline-block;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ecotact</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">hermetic bags for a prolonged shelf life.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What measures do you take to ensure the quality of green coffee is maintained during transit or storage?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">One of the most effective way to maintain the quality and prolong its shelf life is by adopting Ecotact hermetic packaging for our specialty coffee range.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The coffee industry has evolved over the years. Please share some developments that have inspired you?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Over the years it has evolved a lot, for example; direct trade has become very popular, however “true” direct trade with transparency is still difficult to establish. The commercial markets are unfortunately still dominated by the same major players.</span></p>', '2020-08-17', '2021-05-10 14:12:12', '2021-06-22 08:15:47'),
(16, '2', '8', 'Conversaciones en Torno A UN Café Con Hendra Taruli, Directora de Opal Coffee', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Seg&uacute;n usted, </span><strong>&iquest;qu&eacute; cambios se han producido en la industria del caf&eacute; debido a COVID-19? &iquest;Ha repercutido en la forma de operar de Opal Coffee?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">COVID-19 ha tenido un impacto en Opal Coffee de muchas maneras, en la forma en que se llevan a cabo los negocios. Esto incluye varios cambios en la industria. La mayor&iacute;a de los compradores prefieren mantener sus m&eacute;todos de compra anteriores. Mientras el volumen disminuye en el segmento de las especialidades, se ha producido un aumento en el segmento comercial. Con el cambio de los tiempos, los m&eacute;todos tecnol&oacute;gicos tambi&eacute;n se han acelerado.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Ha afectado esto a la demanda de caf&eacute; en los &uacute;ltimos meses?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">El volumen ha disminuido en el segmento de especialidades, mientras que ha aumentado en el segmento comercial.</span></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Opal Coffee opera a nivel mundial. Algunos de sus mercados se han visto afectados de forma moderada y otros se han visto afectados en gran medida por el COVID19. &iquest;Qu&eacute; impacto tiene el mercado del caf&eacute; en cada una de estas regiones? Y el camino a seguir.</span></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">COVID-19 ha impactado de forma diferente, en particular a aquellos negocios que han sido golpeados fuertemente en su volumen. Dado que sus costes fijos permanecen constantes, la mayor&iacute;a de los tostadores optan por reducir el coste de las compras para aumentar su margen bruto y poder pagar los gastos generales fijos.</span></p>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aprovisionamiento de caf&eacute; - </span><strong>&iquest;En qu&eacute; medida es diferente el aprovisionamiento de caf&eacute; en estos tiempos dif&iacute;ciles en los que no es posible visitar el origen? &iquest;En qu&eacute; medida es diferente el abastecimiento de caf&eacute; especial por parte de la industria?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hemos modificado nuestras metodolog&iacute;as anteriores y las relaciones que hemos fomentado. Los proveedores est&aacute;n enviando las muestras en lugar de que nosotros visitemos el origen y, en consecuencia, ha habido algunos retrasos en el proceso de toma de decisiones. Hemos aprovechado este tiempo para establecer nuevas relaciones con nuestros proveedores, ya que antes no ten&iacute;amos la oportunidad de hacerlo.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Cu&aacute;l ha sido el impacto en el precio del caf&eacute; verde, que ya estaba en niveles hist&oacute;ricamente bajos?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">El precio ha estado fluctuando durante mucho tiempo y no ha afectado mucho al precio actual.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;La depreciaci&oacute;n de la moneda de la mayor&iacute;a de los pa&iacute;ses productores ha ayudado a los agricultores locales y a los exportadores de caf&eacute;?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">La depreciaci&oacute;n de la moneda ha afectado sin duda a los peque&ntilde;os productores, pero como la depreciaci&oacute;n de la moneda suele reflejarse en el movimiento del mercado de Nueva York, el precio final de entrega se mantiene m&aacute;s o menos igual.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; puntos hay que tener en cuenta para almacenar los granos de caf&eacute; verde?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cuando se almacena el caf&eacute; hay que hacerlo siempre en un lugar fresco y seco. Adem&aacute;s, debe almacenarse en bolsas herm&eacute;ticas Ecotact para prolongar su vida &uacute;til.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; medidas toman para garantizar que la calidad del caf&eacute; verde se mantenga durante el tr&aacute;nsito o el almacenamiento?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Una de las formas m&aacute;s eficaces de mantener la calidad y prolongar su vida &uacute;til es adoptar los envases herm&eacute;ticos Ecotact para nuestra gama de caf&eacute;s especiales.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>La industria del caf&eacute; ha evolucionado a lo largo de los a&ntilde;os. &iquest;Podr&iacute;a decirnos en qu&eacute; se ha inspirado?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A lo largo de los a&ntilde;os ha evolucionado mucho, por ejemplo, el comercio directo se ha hecho muy popular, aunque el \"verdadero\" comercio directo con transparencia sigue siendo dif&iacute;cil de establecer. Por desgracia, los mercados comerciales siguen dominados por los mismos actores principales.</span></p>', '2020-08-17', '2021-05-10 14:12:12', '2021-06-22 08:15:47'),
(17, '1', '9', 'Q&A with Kyle Bellinger', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">How has the COVID 19 pandemic impacted the Coffee industry?&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Short term, our clients reported business being down by 75-95%.&nbsp; That has slowly started to come back but the long term effects I think that remains to be seen.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are the changes you foresee in terms of trade practices that are going to change and evolve as an aftermath?&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">That’s a tricky one.&nbsp; I think answers would vary depending on the company, its leadership, and how the situation&nbsp;was handled.&nbsp; I know for my own company, we see it as a defining moment in our history where we had the opportunity to back out on many purchase contracts in favor of protecting our own interests but instead opted to follow through with each purchase despite the risk.&nbsp; Our clients have responded favorably to that move and want to support a company that wants to support farmers and partners at origin.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Have you noticed a change in the consumption pattern/demand of Coffee during the pandemic?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Absolutely.&nbsp; The biggest reported by most roasters is that their web sales have skyrocketed.&nbsp; Some have reported as much as a 2500% increase.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are the checks you suggest while sourcing quality coffee?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Across all origins, we measure water activity, moisture content, yield, UV, and cup score.&nbsp; To be honest, while cup score is certainly important we choose not to buy coffees that cup well yet don’t stack up in the other areas.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What would you consider the ideal climate for storage green coffee</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ideal would be frozen temperatures with low humidity haha but I realize that that is not realistic for many. That said, below 60 deg F seems to keep good coffee fresh for quite a long time. I say ‘good coffee’ because bad coffee will fade more quickly no matter what temperature it’s stored at above Should Green Coffee storage be different from Roasted Coffee storage to keep them fresh?</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Should Green Coffee storage be different from Roasted Coffee storage to keep them fresh?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">To be honest, ideal temperatures for both are pretty similar. While freezing in a vacuum-sealed container is ideal for both the warmer it gets the faster each will fade, though roasted coffee obviously fades at a much faster rate than green.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are the best storage solutions for coffee according to you?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Practically speaking, if all of our green coffee was warehoused at a consistent 60 deg F at low humidity and nothing fluctuated, I would be happy. That is, of course, assuming coffees were stored in hermetic bags or vacuum-sealed boxes.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">How do you think hermetic packaging is helping the coffee industry in these difficult times?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">I think a lot of roasters and traders are going to be sitting on coffees for much longer than anticipated and hermetic packaging will absolutely help retain quality and thus value over the next, likely difficult, several months.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Any word of inspiration about coffee and its relationship with its consumers?</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Merriweather, serif; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">These past few months have been the most trying in many of our careers but with strong partners at all links in the supply chain, I think we can all find ways to weather the storm together.</span></p>', '2020-07-04', '2021-05-10 14:16:19', '2021-06-22 08:16:18'),
(18, '2', '9', 'Preguntas y Respuestas Con Kyle Bellinger', '<p><strong>&iquest;C&oacute;mo ha afectado la pandemia de COVID 19 a la industria del caf&eacute;?&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A corto plazo, nuestros clientes informaron de que el negocio hab&iacute;a disminuido entre un 75 y un 95%.&nbsp; Ha empezado a recuperarse poco a poco, pero creo que los efectos a largo plazo est&aacute;n por ver.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Cu&aacute;les son los cambios que prev&eacute; en t&eacute;rminos de pr&aacute;cticas comerciales que van a cambiar y evolucionar como consecuencia?&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Esa es una pregunta complicada.&nbsp; Creo que las respuestas variar&aacute;n en funci&oacute;n de la empresa, de sus dirigentes y de c&oacute;mo se haya gestionado la situaci&oacute;n.&nbsp; S&eacute; que, para mi propia empresa, lo vemos como un momento decisivo en nuestra historia en el que tuvimos la oportunidad de retirarnos de muchos contratos de compra en favor de la protecci&oacute;n de nuestros propios intereses, pero en cambio optamos por seguir adelante con cada compra a pesar del riesgo.&nbsp; Nuestros clientes han respondido favorablemente a esa medida y quieren apoyar a una empresa que quiere apoyar a los agricultores y socios en origen.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Ha notado un cambio en el patr&oacute;n de consumo/demanda de caf&eacute; durante la pandemia?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sin lugar a dudas.&nbsp; Lo que m&aacute;s han comunicado la mayor&iacute;a de los tostadores es que sus ventas por Internet se han disparado.&nbsp; Algunos han informado de un aumento de hasta un 2500%.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Cu&aacute;les son los controles que sugieren a la hora de abastecerse de caf&eacute; de calidad?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">En todos los or&iacute;genes, medimos la actividad del agua, el contenido de humedad, el rendimiento, los rayos UV y la puntuaci&oacute;n en taza.&nbsp; Para ser sinceros, aunque la puntuaci&oacute;n en taza es ciertamente importante, optamos por no comprar caf&eacute;s que tengan una buena taza pero que no se ajusten a las dem&aacute;s &aacute;reas.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Cu&aacute;l es el clima ideal para el almacenamiento de caf&eacute; verde?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&iexcl;Lo ideal ser&iacute;a temperaturas de congelaci&oacute;n con baja humedad&hellip; jaja!!&nbsp; pero me doy cuenta de que eso no es realista para muchos. Dicho esto, por debajo de 60 grados F&deg; parece mantener el buen caf&eacute; fresco durante bastante tiempo. Digo \"buen caf&eacute;\" porque el caf&eacute; malo se desvanecer&aacute; m&aacute;s r&aacute;pidamente sin importar la temperatura a la que se almacene por encima de &iquest;</span><strong>Deber&iacute;a el almacenamiento de caf&eacute; verde ser diferente del almacenamiento de caf&eacute; tostado para mantenerlos frescos?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Debe el almacenamiento del caf&eacute; verde ser diferente del almacenamiento del caf&eacute; tostado para mantenerlo fresco?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Para ser sinceros, las temperaturas ideales para ambos son bastante similares. Mientras que la congelaci&oacute;n en un recipiente sellado al vac&iacute;o es ideal para ambos, cuanto m&aacute;s calor haga, m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido se desvanecer&aacute; cada uno, aunque el caf&eacute; tostado obviamente se desvanece a un ritmo mucho m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido que el verde.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>Seg&uacute;n Ud., &iquest;Cu&aacute;les son las mejores soluciones de almacenamiento para el caf&eacute;?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">En t&eacute;rminos pr&aacute;cticos, si todo nuestro caf&eacute; verde se almacenara a una temperatura constante de 60 grados F&deg; a una humedad baja y nada fluctuara, yo ser&iacute;a feliz. Eso, por supuesto, suponiendo que los caf&eacute;s se almacenaran en bolsas herm&eacute;ticas o en cajas selladas al vac&iacute;o.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;C&oacute;mo cree que el envasado herm&eacute;tico est&aacute; ayudando a la industria del caf&eacute; en estos tiempos dif&iacute;ciles?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creo que muchos tostadores y comercializadores van a tener que guardar los caf&eacute;s durante mucho m&aacute;s tiempo del previsto, y el envasado herm&eacute;tico ayudar&aacute; sin duda a conservar la calidad y, por tanto, el valor durante los pr&oacute;ximos, probablemente dif&iacute;ciles, meses.</span></p>\r\n    <p><strong>&iquest;Alguna palabra de inspiraci&oacute;n sobre el caf&eacute; y su relaci&oacute;n con los consumidores?</strong></p>\r\n    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Estos &uacute;ltimos meses han sido los m&aacute;s dif&iacute;ciles en muchas de nuestras carreras, pero con socios fuertes en todos los eslabones de la cadena de suministro, creo que todos podemos encontrar formas de capear el temporal juntos.</span></p>', '2020-07-04', '2021-05-10 14:16:19', '2021-06-22 08:16:18');
