INSERT INTO `language__blogs` (`id`, `language_id`, `blog_id`, `title`, `desc`, `date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(103, '1', '35', 'Want to Transport Cocoa Beans? Here Are Some Safe Practices to Follow', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Worldwide Favorite</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">It is a truth universally acknowledged that everyone likes chocolate - as a sweet treat, in ointments, balms, or butter. It’s no secret that the world loves chocolate - with the global chocolate market worth US$ 134 Bn. However, even with its universal appeal, chocolate’s main ingredient -cocoa beans- are grown only in subtropical climates: largely in South America and coastal Africa.&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-fe472301-7fff-e703-f63d-5d3a1b0aa76f\"><br></b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">So how do cocoa beans grown in only certain parts of the world reach chocolate lovers everywhere? A delicate transportation process that ensures the aroma and flavor of cocoa beans remain intact through long and arduous journeys.&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cocoa Beans Transportation Tips</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">When shipping cocoa beans it’s important to remember that a lot of external factors like temperature, humidity, moisture, and time will affect your beans. Cocoa beans transportation is a myriad of balances to ensure beans remain fresh even when traveling diverse landscapes.&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Keep it cool</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: The best way to control fluctuating temperatures and humidity levels is to transport beans in a cool and dry environment. Multilayered bags with moisture locks are perfect for this. However, it’s imperative to ensure the cool temperature doesn’t turn cold as that could be harmful to the beans as well.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\" start=\"2\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">No moisture allowed</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: The best yardstick to ensure the quality of cocoa beans is to keep its Free Fatty Acid (FFA) levels even. When moisture interacts with beans they tend to raise FFA levels which can leave it tasting acidic and affect its quality.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\" start=\"3\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Airtight is the answer</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: An airtight or vacuum-packed bag is the best way to ensure no external elements harm your beans. Be it moisture, humidity, insects, rodents, or more. The best way to lock in the fresh flavor and aroma is by investing in the right hermetic packaging.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Packed and Ready For Travel&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cocoa beans transportation takes place over sea and land. This is why different vehicles require different precautions:&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">By sea</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: In case packed in cargo ships, the beans need to be stored below decks away from any heat source.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\" start=\"2\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">By land</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">: In case of being transported across land, it\'s important to keep your cargo in closed compartments of the vehicle.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">How To Prevent Transportation Problems</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">It’s important to keep your cocoa beans secure through their journey.&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Monitor weather conditions of areas of travel&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ensure water levels are below 8% at all times&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Ensure storage space is dry and cool&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Keep rodents and pests away from where the beans are stored</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Use packaging that is sturdy and airtight&nbsp;</span></p></li></ul><p><b style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><br></b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">How Ecotact Helps&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Bookman Old Style\',serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Packaging is essential to cocoa bean transportation. Hermetic packaging that is airtight with moisture locks is what helps humidity and temperature levels remain stable. This retains the farm freshness of cocoa beans even as they travel halfway across the world. Ecotact is a global coffee packaging supplier and coffee bag manufacturer that offers multilayered hermetic biodegradable coffee bags. Our vacuum-sealed coffee bags are the perfect packaging solution for cocoa beans. Enjoy high-quality delicious chocolate from anywhere in the world with the best coffee packaging for your beans!</span></p><p></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Georgia;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Looks good! We may add link to our website</span></p><div><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Georgia;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></div>', '25th December, 2021', '2022-02-25 17:40:56', '2022-02-25 17:40:56'),
