(38, 2, 'Ecotact Ship Shield Hermetic Container Liners', 4, 'English', 'Product Details of Ecotact Ship Shield Hermetic Container Liners', 'High-tech Ship Shield Hermetic Container Liner is designed to store and transport grains in a hermetically sealed structure. Manufactured in a cleanroom facility and meeting FDA standards, this ISO 22000:2018, ISO 9001:2015, bags come with high barrier properties which keep the aroma and the moisture content of the grain intact.', NULL, 'Ecotact Ship Shield Hermetic Container Liners | Shipping Grains', 'Ecotact has Ship shield hermetic container liners to store and transport grains, green coffee, and cocoa in sealed packaging with high barrier properties while shipping.', 'Ship Shield Hermetic Container Liners', '2021-04-17 05:49:23', '2022-08-26 14:15:22'),
(39, 3, 'Ecotact Multilayered Hermetic Storage Bags', 4, 'English', 'Product Details of Multilayered Hermetic Storage Bags - Green Coffee & Cacao Sacks', 'The ecological plastic bags inside burlap bags are extremely strong and have high oxygen and moisture barrier properties to seal the freshness of green coffee throughout the supply chain and storage.', NULL, 'Ecotact Multilayered Hermetic Storage Bags | Coffee & Cacao Sacks', 'Ecotact delivers multilayered hermetic storage bags globally. Our green coffee storage bags, grain & cacao sacks maintain quality with high oxygen & moisture barrier.', 'Multilayered Hermetic Storage Bags,  hermetic storage bags,  Cacao sack', '2021-04-17 06:33:36', '2022-08-19 15:38:58'),
(40, 4, 'Ecotact Hermetic FIBC Bags', 4, 'English', 'Product Details of Ecotact Hermetic FIBC storage bags', 'Ecotact Hermetic Flexible Intermediate Bulk Container Bags are high quality polypropylene bags with multilayered high capacity hermetic plastic liners inside for efficient storage and transportation of coffee in bulk.', NULL, 'Buy The Best Ecotact Hermetic FIBC Storage Bags | FIBC Bulk Bags', 'Our FIBC storage Bags have multilayered high-capacity hermetic plastic for efficient storage & transportation of green coffee, cocoa and beans. Order FIBC bulk bags.', 'fibc storage bags, fibc bags', '2021-04-17 06:39:34', '2022-08-18 15:38:31'),
