(42, 6, 'Ecotact Troiseal Bags', 4, 'English', 'Product Details of Ecotact Troiseal Packaging Bags for Coffee Beans and Other Grains', 'These are tamper-proof hermetically sealed bags designed especially for green coffee &amp; other coffee beans. The flexibility of the bag makes it a perfect match for small and homegrown roasters.', NULL, 'Best Ecotact Troiseal Bags | Buy Reusable Green Coffee Bags', 'Ecotact Troiseal packaging bags are tamper-proof, resealable & reusable green coffee bags especially designed for storing coffee beans, cacao, grains, etc. Shop now!', 'ecotact troiseal bags, reusable coffee bags, Resealable bags, reusable bags', '2021-04-17 06:46:56', '2022-11-22 16:16:15'),
