(49, 13, 'ECOVAC 20-2', 1, 'English', 'Product Details of ECOVAC 20-2 - Vacuum Packaging Equipment', 'A robust blend of advanced technology and outstanding innovation. ECOVAC 20-2 is a powerful STRAIGHT CHAMBER VACUUM MACHINE with durability, power and seal compression with utmost ease.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Crafted with advanced technology, innovative \r\ncontrol system and a modern design, this machine provides the best \r\nprecise vacuum packaging. <br><br>Accepting various sizes for vacuuming,\r\n starting from 10 kilograms of food grains up to 20 kilograms, ECOVAC \r\n20-2 is definitely the most economical way of precision packaging for \r\nlong term storage and transportation of food grains. This machine helps \r\nfood grains remain in farm fresh dried condition, keeping the aroma and \r\nmoisture levels intact for a long duration.<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">SPECIFICATIONS</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">SIZE OF THE MACHINE</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Machine Size </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Sealing bar length of 700 mm. </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">• Over-all size </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Width 950 mm, Depth 980 mm, Height 1310 mm. ECOVAC 20-2\r\naccepts various sizes for vacuuming starting from 10 kilograms of food grains\r\nto 20 Kilograms of it.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>NOTE: No compressor is required to run this machine.</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Vacuum Packaging involves placing items in a plastic film\r\npackage (Manually or automatically), removing air from inside (Mostly\r\natmospheric oxygen) and sealing the package. With vacuum packaging you can: </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/bullet-check.svg\" alt=\"Bullet Check Icon\" class=\"bullet-pointer\">&nbsp; Extend the shelf life of grains </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"https://www.ecotactbags.com/front-end/images/bullet-check.svg\" alt=\"Bullet Check Ico